    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to zigzag or wriggled grooves found on the underside of silver pieces (Continental or Scottish but rarely English) formed when samples of the metal were taken for assaying. The marks often resemble the letter N or Z but no significance can be attached to their form.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000011151/Fleming and Honour, Penguin Dictionary of the Decorative Arts (1989)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Verwijst naar groeven in zigzag- of golfvorm aan de onderzijde van (Europees of Schots, maar zelden Engels) zilverwerk, die zijn aangebracht bij het nemen van metaalmonsters voor testdoeleinden. De tekens lijken vaak op de letter N of Z, maar aan de vorm kan geen betekenis worden ontleend.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052669/Baarsen, Rijksmuseum Zilverwerk,</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>指當銀器樣本送檢時，其底部所產生的Z字型或彎曲溝紋。常見於歐陸或蘇格蘭，但英國則罕見。該標記通常類似字母N或Z，但並無特別含義。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
